import React from 'react';
import { Button, Dialog, Flex, Text } from '@radix-ui/themes';
import { User } from '../../types/User';

const DeleteUserModal: React.FC<any> = ({user, isOpen, onClose}:{user: User, isOpen: boolean, onClose: () => void}) => {
  return (
    <Dialog.Root open={isOpen} onOpenChange={onClose}>
      <Dialog.Content maxWidth="450px">
        <Dialog.Title>Delete user</Dialog.Title>
        <Dialog.Description>
          {user ? 
          <>
          <Text>
            Are you sure? The user{" "} 
            </Text>
            <Text weight="bold">
            {user.first} {user.last}{" "}
              </Text> 
              <Text>
            will be perminently deleted.
            </Text>
          </>
          :
          <></>
        }
          </Dialog.Description>
        <Flex gap="3" mt="4" justify="end">
          <Dialog.Close>
            <Button variant="soft" color="gray">
              Cancel
            </Button>
          </Dialog.Close>
          <Dialog.Close>
            <Button color="ruby" variant="surface">Delete user</Button>
          </Dialog.Close>
        </Flex>
      </Dialog.Content>
    </Dialog.Root>
  )
}

export default DeleteUserModal;
